<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
<meta charset="UTF-8">
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
<title>Colour Trading Platform</title>

<link href="https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Poppins:wght@300;500;700&display=swap" rel="stylesheet">

<style>
*{
    margin:0;
    padding:0;
    box-sizing:border-box;
    font-family:'Poppins',sans-serif;
}

body{
    min-height:100vh;
    background:linear-gradient(-45deg,#0f2027,#1c1c3c,#203a43,#000000);
    background-size:400% 400%;
    animation:bgMove 12s ease infinite;
    display:flex;
    justify-content:center;
    align-items:center;
    color:white;
}

@keyframes bgMove{
    0%{background-position:0% 50%;}
    50%{background-position:100% 50%;}
    100%{background-position:0% 50%;}
}

.container{
    background:rgba(255,255,255,0.05);
    padding:35px;
    border-radius:20px;
    backdrop-filter:blur(15px);
    box-shadow:0 0 40px rgba(0,255,255,0.25);
    max-width:450px;
    width:92%;
    text-align:center;
}

.logo{
    font-size:28px;
    font-weight:700;
    color:#00f7ff;
    margin-bottom:8px;
}

.tagline{
    font-size:14px;
    margin-bottom:20px;
    opacity:0.8;
}

.trading-box{
    margin:20px 0;
    padding:18px;
    background:rgba(0,255,255,0.07);
    border-radius:15px;
    border:1px solid rgba(0,255,255,0.3);
    text-align:left;
}

.trading-box h3{
    color:#00f7ff;
    margin-bottom:10px;
    text-align:center;
}

.trading-box p{
    font-size:13px;
    line-height:1.6;
    opacity:0.9;
}

.points{
    margin-top:12px;
    font-size:13px;
}

.note{
    margin-top:12px;
    font-size:12px;
    opacity:0.65;
}

.btn{
    display:block;
    width:100%;
    padding:12px;
    margin-top:15px;
    border:none;
    border-radius:30px;
    font-size:16px;
    font-weight:500;
    cursor:pointer;
    transition:0.3s;
    text-decoration:none;
    text-align:center;
}

.primary{
    background:#00f7ff;
    color:black;
    box-shadow:0 0 15px #00f7ff;
}

.primary:hover{
    transform:scale(1.05);
    box-shadow:0 0 25px #00f7ff;
}

.footer{
    margin-top:18px;
    font-size:12px;
    opacity:0.6;
}
</style>
</head>

<body>

<div class="container">

    <div class="logo">COLOUR TRADING</div>
    <div class="tagline">Smart Strategy • Controlled Risk • Better Planning</div>

    <div class="trading-box">
        <h3>About Colour Trading</h3>
        <p>
            Colour trading ek fast-paced prediction based activity hai jahan users 
            trend aur pattern observation ke basis par decision lete hain. 
            Isme disciplined strategy aur risk management bahut important hota hai.
        </p>

        <div class="points">
            ✔ Real-Time Trend Observation <br>
            ✔ Smart Entry & Exit Planning <br>
            ✔ Capital Protection Strategy <br>
            ✔ Long-Term Stability Focus
        </div>

        <div class="note">
            Note: Trading activities me financial risk shamil hota hai. 
            Hamesha responsible approach follow karein.
        </div>
    </div>

    <!-- JOIN BUTTON WITH TELEGRAM LINK -->
    <a href="https://t.me/+h1z0MsHsDhg1MTU9" target="_blank" class="btn primary">
        JOIN NOW
    </a>

    <div class="footer">
        © 2026 Colour Trading Platform | Play Responsibly
    </div>

</div>

</body>
</html>